{
  "stem": "5740.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- I think she was the daughter of a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she went to her-- she was working as a tailoress.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she said, [NON-ENGLISH], pray for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The, the, yeah, the Lagerfuhrerin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She ran away, but they caught her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know much about it, because I didn't want-- I, I, I didn't want any revenge.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't want to see anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was just happy to be, to be free.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russians.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Russians arrived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They arrived, and they said that we can go out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they opened all the stores and to take food and to take clothes, and-- and, you know, there was medicine for the sick ones.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and, and there was nobody in the camp, you know, nobody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could do what we wanted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I wanted, I wanted to find somebody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I wanted to know if anybody of my people are alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So and I saw that were coming to our camps also, boys from other camps, you know, that they survived and are looking for sisters, for somebody.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And once, a group of them came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I asked, look, do you know anybody by the name Majerczyk?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, yes, in Waldenburg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So not thinking of nothing, I left [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I left everybody, and I hitchhiked to Waldenburg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there I found two cousins of mine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they lived over there in a, in a flat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In Waldenburg?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Waldenburg.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was still May, 1945.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stayed with them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there I met my husband.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My husband comes from Vienna.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he will, he will tell you his story separately.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as it happened, he was in the concentration camp together with my cousins.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I didn't meet him through my cousins.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
